Resource Profile: Case Based Surveillance Composition Profile

Defining URL:http://cbsig.chai.gatech.edu/StructureDefinition/cbs-composition
Version:0.1.0
Name:CaseBasedSurveillanceComposition
Title:Case Based Surveillance Composition Profile
Status:Experimental as of 2021-01-01
Definition:

Defines constraints to the Composition resource in order to meet the needs of public health surveillance programs.

Publisher:Georgia Tech Research Institute (GTRI)
Source Resource:XML / JSON / Turtle

The official URL for this profile is: 

http://cbsig.chai.gatech.edu/StructureDefinition/cbs-composition

Description of Profiles, Differentials, Snapshots and how the different presentations work.
